283
00:26:06,147 --> 00:26:08,275
Do you feel the same way about me?

284
00:26:16,324 --> 00:26:18,159
You really love leading people on, Mikoy.

285
00:26:18,243 --> 00:26:19,786
<i>Such a heartbreaker.</i>
